    {
      "text": "Become a Secret Sleuth! Embark on a strange and mysterious journey in the newest detective game designed especially for kids! Junior Mystery Quest puts you in the middle of a captivating conspiracy, where the Tibutto family must solve the puzzle of their missing Uncle Alester. With challenges hidden around every corner, children must put their problem-solving skills to the test!",
